    {
      "author": "Dhoni G. Daradjat",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107870160684225108303?hl=id",
      "rating": 1,
      "text": "Only 20 % from the menu  is available to order. When i got there no one else is eating there, but it took 20ish minute to prepare 2 simple dish (chicken + rice).  The disappointment still there when we eat it and found out the rice is not fully cooked (gigih). Definitely wont come again..",
      "textTranslated": "Hanya 20% dari menu yang tersedia untuk dipesan. Ketika saya tiba di sana, tidak ada orang lain yang makan di sana, tetapi butuh waktu sekitar 20 menit untuk menyiapkan 2 hidangan sederhana (ayam + nasi). Kekecewaan masih terasa ketika kami memakannya dan ternyata nasinya belum matang sempurna (gigih). Pasti tidak akan kembali lagi.",
